high_descs: Walk towards the stools and make a left at the refrigerator and a right at the dishwasher,
Pick up the cooking pot, on the back left burner of the stove.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Place the cooking pot on the second shelf, to the right of the tomato, in the refrigerator, wait a moment for it to chill, then remove the cooking pot from the refrigerator.
Turn to your right and go to the counter with the coffee maker and toaster on it.
Place the cooking pot between the dog statue and the toaster, on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cooking pot on the counter.

high_descs: move to the stove to the right of the sink
pick up a pot from the stove
move to the fridge behind you
chill the pot in the fridge for a moment
move to the counter to the left of the stove
put the pot on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pot on a counter.

high_descs: Walk to the stove on your right.
Grab the pot off the stove.
Walk to the front of the fridge.
Place the pot in the fridge, close the fridge, then open the fridge and grab the pot.
Walk to the corner of the kitchen counter.
Place the pot in the bottom right cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Chill a pot and put it in a cabinet.
